"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Free.html#FreeMagma\">FreeMagma</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Free.html#FreeMagma\">FreeMagma</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Free.html#FreeMagma\">FreeMagma</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Mathlib/Algebra/Free.html#FreeMagma.mul","kind":"ctor","line":80,"name":"FreeMagma.mul","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Algebra/Free.lean#L80-L80"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Free.html#FreeMagma.of\"><span class=\"name\">FreeMagma</span>.<span class=\"name\">of</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Free.html#FreeMagma\">FreeMagma</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Mathlib/Algebra/Free.html#FreeMagma.of","kind":"ctor","line":79,"name":"FreeMagma.of","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Algebra/Free.lean#L79-L79"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">inductive</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Free.html#FreeMagma\"><span class=\"name\">FreeMagma</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u</div></div>","info":{"doc":"If `α` is a type, then `FreeMagma α` is the free magma generated by `α`.\nThis is a magma equipped with a function `FreeMagma.of : α → FreeMagma α` which has\nthe following universal property: if `M` is any magma, and `f : α → M` is any function,\nthen this function is the composite of `FreeMagma.of` and a unique multiplicative homomorphism\n`FreeMagma.lift f : FreeMagma α →ₙ* M`.\n\nA typical element of `FreeMagma α` is a formal non-associative product of\nelements of `α`. For example if `x` and `y` are terms of type `α` then `x * ((y * y) * x)` is a\n\"typical\" element of `FreeMagma α`.\nOne can think of `FreeMagma α` as the type of binary trees with leaves labelled by `α`.\nIn general, no pair of distinct elements in `FreeMagma α` will commute.\n","docLink":"./Mathlib/Algebra/Free.html#FreeMagma","kind":"inductive","line":64,"name":"FreeMagma","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Algebra/Free.lean#L64-L81"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">instance</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Free.html#instDecidableEqFreeAddMagma\"><span class=\"name\">instDecidableEqFreeAddMagma</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α✝</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#DecidableEq\">DecidableEq</a> <span class=\"fn\">α✝</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#DecidableEq\">DecidableEq</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Free.html#FreeAddMagma\">FreeAddMagma</a> <span class=\"fn\">α✝</span>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Mathlib/Algebra/Free.html#instDecidableEqFreeAddMagma","kind":"instance","line":57,"name":"instDecidableEqFreeAddMagma","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Algebra/Free.lean#L57-L57"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Free.html#instDecidableEqFreeAddMagma.decEq\"><span class=\"name\">instDecidableEqFreeAddMagma</span>.<span class=\"name\">decEq</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α✝</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u_1}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">[<span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#DecidableEq\">DecidableEq</a> <span class=\"fn\">α✝</span></span>]</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">x✝ </span><span class=\"fn\">x✝¹</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Free.html#FreeAddMagma\">FreeAddMagma</a> <span class=\"fn\">α✝</span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Decidable\">Decidable</a> (<span class=\"fn\">x✝</span> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Eq\">=</a> <span class=\"fn\">x✝¹</span>)</span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Mathlib/Algebra/Free.html#instDecidableEqFreeAddMagma.decEq","kind":"def","line":57,"name":"instDecidableEqFreeAddMagma.decEq","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Algebra/Free.lean#L57-L57"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Free.html#FreeAddMagma.add\"><span class=\"name\">FreeAddMagma</span>.<span class=\"name\">add</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Free.html#FreeAddMagma\">FreeAddMagma</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Free.html#FreeAddMagma\">FreeAddMagma</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Free.html#FreeAddMagma\">FreeAddMagma</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Mathlib/Algebra/Free.html#FreeAddMagma.add","kind":"ctor","line":56,"name":"FreeAddMagma.add","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Algebra/Free.lean#L56-L56"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Free.html#FreeAddMagma.of\"><span class=\"name\">FreeAddMagma</span>.<span class=\"name\">of</span></a></span><span class=\"impl_arg\"><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">{<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u}</span></span>\n</span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><span class=\"fn\">α</span> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Free.html#FreeAddMagma\">FreeAddMagma</a> <span class=\"fn\">α</span></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Mathlib/Algebra/Free.html#FreeAddMagma.of","kind":"ctor","line":55,"name":"FreeAddMagma.of","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Algebra/Free.lean#L55-L55"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">inductive</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/Algebra/Free.html#FreeAddMagma\"><span class=\"name\">FreeAddMagma</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">α</span> : <a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> u</div></div>","info":{"doc":"If `α` is a type, then `FreeAddMagma α` is the free additive magma generated by `α`.\nThis is an additive magma equipped with a function `FreeAddMagma.of : α → FreeAddMagma α` which has\nthe following universal property: if `M` is any magma, and `f : α → M` is any function,\nthen this function is the composite of `FreeAddMagma.of` and a unique additive homomorphism\n`FreeAddMagma.lift f : FreeAddMagma α →ₙ+ M`.\n\nA typical element of `FreeAddMagma α` is a formal non-associative sum of\nelements of `α`. For example if `x` and `y` are terms of type `α` then `x + ((y + y) + x)` is a\n\"typical\" element of `FreeAddMagma α`.\nOne can think of `FreeAddMagma α` as the type of binary trees with leaves labelled by `α`.\nIn general, no pair of distinct elements in `FreeAddMagma α` will commute.\n","docLink":"./Mathlib/Algebra/Free.html#FreeAddMagma","kind":"inductive","line":41,"name":"FreeAddMagma","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/Algebra/Free.lean#L41-L57"}}],"imports":["Init","Mathlib.Algebra.Group.Basic","Mathlib.Algebra.Group.Equiv.Defs","Mathlib.Control.Applicative","Mathlib.Control.Traversable.Basic","Mathlib.Logic.Equiv.Defs","Mathlib.Tactic.AdaptationNote","Mathlib.Tactic.Attr.Register"],"insta